webchem 0.0.2
======================

NEW FEATURES

* Query the PAN Pesticides Database with pan().

MINOR IMPROVEMENTS

* Added some checks for user input.
* fixed documentation.
* cts_convert() returns NA if no result was found.
* set verbose = TRUE as default for all functions.

BUG FIXES

* cts_convert() does not ignore 'first' argument.
* get_csid() did not return NA, if there is a problem with the webservice.
* cir_query() returned NA2+ if NA was given.
* Many fixes in handling NA, when no hit was found.